      <p><strong>Policy Title:</strong> Examination Policy (EP)</p>
      <p><strong>Policy Number:</strong> EP-PO-3L</p>
      <p><strong>Date Created:</strong> 12-08-2008</p>
      <p><strong>Responsible:</strong> Registrar</p>
